annotationA: Ribosomal protein L21, isoform A; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization
annotationB: 60S acidic ribosomal protein P0; Ribosomal protein P0 is the functional equivalent of E.coli protein L10; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL10 family
